The rules of the Void are determined by the strong.

511
00:39:47,860 --> 00:39:51,440
If I can resist your moves with my medical skills,

512
00:39:51,440 --> 00:39:54,100
that proves that the Void should not consider medical treatment a taboo.

513
00:39:54,100 --> 00:39:57,020
And Third Prince should not be wronged for seeking medical attention.

514
